high_descs: Turn right and walk to the middle of a corridor, then go left where you see a kitchen sink.
Pick up the bowl from next to the sink.
Approach the fridge that is opposite to the sink.
Place the bowl in the fridge, let it cool inside for a while, then take the bowl out.
Walk back to the middle of the corridor, then go right through the exit and right again until you reach a round diningtable.
Put the bowl on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled bowl on the diningtable.

high_descs: walk straight and left towards the sink
pick up the bowl from the sink
cool the bowl in the fridge
turn right and walk straight towards the dining table
place the bowl on the table
anns.task_desc: cool the bowl in the fridge and place the bowl on the table

high_descs: Turn right and walk down the hallway, then go to the sink to your left
Pick up the bowl on the sink
Put the bowl on the bottom shelf of the fridge, cool it, get the bowl out of the fridge
Turn left and walk down the hallway on your right towards the shelf to your left, then hang a right and walk to dining table
Put the bowl on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl on a dining table
